    {
      "headings": [
        {
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "Gain in-depth Insights into your Farm Business"
        }
      ],
      "paragraphs": [
        "With our detailed pre-built agriculture data analytics dashboard, you will be able to gain crucial insights such as:",
        "With our detailed pre-built agriculture data analytics dashboard, \nyou will be able to gain crucial insights such as:"
      ],
      "listItems": [
        "What are your on-going operations and their current status",
        "Water Consumption for each crop type",
        "What was each employee’s productivity to determine labor cost.",
        "Identify reserved and available machinery to plan your next activities.",
        "What are your most profitable and least profitable crops in each season?",
        "Budgeted vs Actual cost consumed by each crop during a season to access your financial targets.",
        "Quantity of each resource such as fertilizer, pesticides, etc, were consumed by a crop.",
        "Based on historical data, calculate forecasted yield and compare with actual annual yield.",
        "Forecasted demand for upcoming season to plan your yield accordingly."
      ],
      "ctas": [
        {
          "text": "Speak to Our Experts",
          "href": "#pgForm"
        }
      ],
      "images": []
    },
